<section>
    The calculator is a highly reliable emulator for BA II Plus Professional Financial Calculator on iPhone and iPad. It's perfect
    for students, teachers, professionals and people who are preparing for CFA® or FRM®. The app has built-in tutorials and
    supports landscape mode, sound and vibration (iPhone).
</section>

<section>
    The calculator is ideal for applications in finance, accounting, economics, investment, statistics, and more. 
    Excellent mortgage calculator and loan calculator.
</section>

<h2>Features:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Time-Value-of-Money (TVM)</li>
  <li>Net Present Value (NPV)</li>
  <li>Modified Internal Rate of Return (MIRR)</li>
  <li>Bond Price, Accrued Interest and Modified Duration. </li>
  <li>Amortization</li>
  <li>Cost-Sell-Margin</li>
  <li>Depreciation</li>
  <li>Statistical Analysis</li>
  <li>Currency Converter</li>
  <li>30/360, Actual/360 day-count methods</li>
  <li>Profit Margin</li>
  <li>Breakeven</li>
  <li>Interest Conversion</li>
  <li>Percent Change/Compound Interest</li>
  <li>Choice of Chain and Algebraic Operating System methods</li>
  <li>Memory values </li>
</ul>

